8. the room database can have entity, dao and database
9. the tasks data are reactive
10. a alert dialog box to confirm the exit of the app if double pressed which is placed in the task baar
11. add constants were ever possible
12. use default app icons
13. use singleton for database initialization
14. separate thread for db and ui
15. on clicking the fab a bottom sheet dialog box should open with editing keyboard of the phone simultaneously
16. bottom should dialog should have a title , description and option to select it is starred or not
17. use scope function let and apply if possible
